data.description: Located in a quiet area and just walking distance to Tibby Elementary School, this cute 2 bedrooms and 1 bath home with almost seven thousand  lot size comes with hardwood flooring, kitchen with laundry area has granite counters, tile floors in bathroom,carpet in bedrooms.  You will love the quiet neighborhood!  Sellers purchase this property back in 2014 with new windows throughout, new plumbing, new water heater and brand new roof installed.
